Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:22.87,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{God...}Thần linh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:48.05,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Damn it. That really hurt, you asshole!}Thằng khốn, đau đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:51.93,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{You're a lot stronger than I had thought.}Ngươi mạnh hơn ta nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.93,0:00:54.28,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{This might be quite the workout \Nfor an old timer like me.}Có vẻ tuổi già đã ảnh hưởng đến ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:59.78,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{Go ahead. Come at me again. Or would you \Nrather run crying to your friend?}Lên đi. Hay cứ bỏ chạy đến chỗ bạn ngươi cũng được.
