Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:39.51,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{This is so irritating...}Phiền thật...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:46.64,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{I don't think they'll be \Ncoming back this time.}Chắc lần này hết hồi sinh lại rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:49.73,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Did she do all that by swinging a sword?!}Chỉ vung kiếm thôi á?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:53.65,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{What the hell?! How big of a \Nmonster can one person be?!}Cái quái gì vậy? Thứ quái vật này mạnh đến cỡ nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:57.92,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Still, I knew from the beginning \Nthat I couldn't win...}Nhưng mình cũng biết là không thể thắng rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:00.35,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Let's see how much time of yours I can waste.}Để xem câu giờ được bao lâu nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:05.12,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Damn it. What are these blasted strings?!}Chết tiệt. Đám chỉ này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:09.54,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Looking a bit more closely, \Nthe strings are attached to them...}Nhìn kĩ thì cơ thể chúng cũng có chỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:14.04,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Maybe they're all being controlled \Nby a main body, somewhere else?}Vậy là được điều khiển bởi kẻ khác?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:18.95,Main,Decoy 2,0,0,0,,{That's right! What you've been \Nfighting are merely my marionettes!}Chính xác đấy. Ngươi đang chiến đấu với mấy con rối của ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:22.30,Main,Decoy 2,0,0,0,,{You have to defeat me if you \Nwant to end this battle!}Phải đánh bại ta nếu muốn kết thúc trận chiến.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.06,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Then you're the one behind this!}Vậy ra là ngươi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.02,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{My face! Ow, my face!}Đau quá! Mặt mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:32.88,Main,Decoy 2,0,0,0,,{You fell right for that one!}Trúng bẫy rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:34.48,Main,Decoy 2,0,0,0,,{I think I'll call it the \NNetted Face Shredder!}Ngươi sẽ là con nhỏ mặt lưới!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:36.90,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{I've had enough of this—}Đủ rồi đấy--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:39.07,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{What the?!}Cái quái?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:41.32,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{My arm just flew off!}Tay mình vừa bị chặt đứt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:45.05,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{She is... incredibly good \Nat falling for traps.}Cô ta... dễ dàng bị dính bẫy nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:46.78,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Could I...}Liệu có thể...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.29,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{actually win this, if I play my cards right?}đánh bại cô ta nếu mình biết cách?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:53.82,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Another day, another search for \Nbaldy Barcode, the giant old lady,}Bao nhiêu ngày đã qua tìm kiếm Barcode, bà già to con,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:56.43,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{and the pigtailed bondage gal.}và con gal hai bím vếu bự rồi?
