Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:05.19,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,{to his PC at home, which is then \Ndisplayed for General Piscalat.}đến PC ở nhà, và hiển thị cho Piscalat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.06,Main - Top,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{No. No. No.}Không. Không. Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:09.06,Main - Top,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{No.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:13.29,Main - Top,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{No. No. No. No.}{No. No. No.}Không. Không. Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:13.91,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Is it me, or are you treating \Nthis like an assembly line worker}Do mình tưởng tượng hay đúng là đang bị bắt làm việc
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:15.06,Main - Top,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{No. No.}{No. No. No.}Không. Không. Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:15.06,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{who's looking for faulty products?}để tìm sản phẩm lỗi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:16.84,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Pipe down.}Im lặng đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.73,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Wait, how many people resembling \NMiku have you seen?}Khoan, anh thấy bao nhiêu Miku rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:22.58,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Only the one.}Chỉ có một.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:26.49,Main,Card sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HB2B5B5&\bord2\shad0\3c&HE9ECEB&\frz18.67\fs18\pos(218.667,96.666)}{Miku}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:26.49,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{I doubt there's a lot of people \Nwith that kind of fashion sense.}Làm gì có ai ăn mặc giống vậy nữa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:29.78,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Exactly. So, how do you explain her?}Chính xác. Vậy cô ta trông thế nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:32.09,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{It's a bit too exact to \Njust be a coincidence.}Quá khó tin khi đó là ngẫu nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:33.76,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{A decoy?}Cò mồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:36.86,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{Yeah. The question is, why?}Phải. Câu hỏi là tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:39.44,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Okay, I'll go have a chat with her.}Rồi, tôi sẽ xuống gặp cô ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:43.76,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{I need to borrow you for a sec.}Mượn bé chút nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:44.95,Main,Decoy,0,0,0,,{Excuse me?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:49.18,Main,Decoy,0,0,0,,{What is this?! What is this?!}Cái gì thế? Cái gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.48,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Stop screaming!}Đừng có la nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:53.64,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{If you're human, you won't be harmed, \Nso simmer down a little!}Nếu là người thì yên tâm đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.09,0:05:03.81,Main,Prisoner,0,0,0,,{We need to get out of here!}Chúng ta chạy mau thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:05.20,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{No. I...}Không, tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:08.70,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I'm going to bear witness to this.}Phải chứng kiến trận chiến này.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:18.25,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Come on, pops, you're not gonna sprout \Ntentacles or shapeshift or anything?}Này lão già, lão không mọc\N xúc tu hay thay đổi hình dạng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:21.02,Italics,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{He regenerates too fast.}Nó hồi phục quá nhanh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:23.30,Italics,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{The longer this goes on, \Nthe more of a disadvantage for me.}Đánh càng lâu mình càng bất lợi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:35.31,sign_4605_28__1_Peacetime,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)\c&HC2249F&\fs30\pos(330,228.667)\bord0\frx60}#8 Idaten
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:28.10,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{I can't do that. \NI'm just good in a straight-up fight.}Ta không thể. Ta chỉ cứ thế mà đánh thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:31.84,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{Which I imagine suits you perfectly. \NNo tricks or gimmicks involved.}Nhưng rất hợp với ngươi còn gì. \NMột trận chiến không tính toán.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.61,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{True enough.}Cũng đúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:34.75,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Let's do this!}Vậy chiến thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:38.26,Italics,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{I'd have no chance if he \Ncapitalized on his speed}Mình sẽ không thể thắng nếu nó cứ hồi phục như vậy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:40.18,Italics,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{and healing to draw the battle out...}và tiếp tục trận chiến...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:41.36,Italics,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{What a simpleton.}Thật dễ dàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:48.98,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{You didn't need to come here. \NYour side would've won the war, either way.}Ngươi không cần phải đến đâu. \NTrước sau gì các ngươi chả thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:54.04,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Screw that. You expect me to hide \Nbehind Granny my whole life?}Ngươi nghĩ ta sẽ cứ dựa vào bà già chết tiệt đó mãi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:59.79,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{By the way, you sure you don't \Nwanna pull that arm out, pops?!}Cơ mà cứ để tay như vậy ổn không, lão già?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:04.59,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Shit, this actually hurts really bad.}Chết tiệt, đau đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:08.22,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{You take a wound like that, \Nand it only hurts?}Nhận vết thương chí mạng và chỉ đau?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:11.18,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{You're not done yet, are you?}Vẫn chưa xong đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:13.59,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{No. Come at me.}Ờ, đến đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.96,Italics,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{I think this is as far as I go...}Có vẻ chỉ đến đây thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.73,Main,Decoy 2,0,0,0,,{Hey, what's wrong? You dead?}Này sao thế? Chết rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:24.40,Main,Decoy 2,0,0,0,,{Why don't you try and get me again?}Mau đến bắt ta đi nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:31.37,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{I came out here half ready to die, \Nbut I think I might actually pull this off.}Mình đã cắt gần hết tứ chi. Hay là phanh thây luôn?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.58,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Damn you...}Chết tiệt...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:41.37,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Your roundabout way of fighting is \Nstarting to seriously tick me off!}Chiến đấu một cách rườm rà khiến ta bực rồi đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:45.68,Italics,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Wait, what?! What the hell?! \NHow did she regenerate so quickly?!}Hả? Cái quái gì thế? Cái thể loại hồi phục gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:51.22,Main,Decoy,0,0,0,,{What are you trying to do by \Ngetting wound up yourself?}Vừa tự hồi phục xong lại làm mình bị thương?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.91,Main,Decoy,0,0,0,,{You can't even use that sword, now!}Và cũng không còn dùng kiếm được nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:57.35,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Really? Then maybe I'll get \Na little more wound up!}Thật à? Vậy thì ta sẽ chịu thêm ít vết thương nữa vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:06.94,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Th-This is bad! I have to untangle my hair and—}T-Tệ quá! Phải cắt tóc ngay--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:15.54,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{That should be all of the decoys, \Nalong with the real body.}Chắc chắn đây là đống hàng giả và cả hàng thật nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:19.58,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{And now I'll cut through it all at once!}Giờ thì ta sẽ thổi bay 1 lần!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.71,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Master is really going wild out there.}Sư phụ lại làm quá rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:34.25,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{You seem to be the only one left.}Tên duy nhất còn lại nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:36.20,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Are you the real body?}Cơ thể thực hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:44.48,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Looks like you're done...}Có vẻ xong rồi à...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.97,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Then I win.}Ta thắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:52.68,Italics,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{Good grief... he actually ran \Noff, without finishing me.}Chết tiệt... Hắn bỏ đi mà không kết thúc mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:56.58,Italics,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{It seems he only cares about \Nwhether he wins or not.}Có vẻ hắn chỉ quan tâm đến thắng thua.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:08:01.33,Flashback,Obami,0,0,0,,{I'd recommend preparing \Na nuclear missile launch.}Ta khuyên cậu nên chuẩn bị phóng tên lửa hạt nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:06.29,Flashback,Obami,0,0,0,,{Although even if it's effective, \Nwe'd still end up dying in the process...}Dù nó cũng chả có hiệu quả mấy, \Nchúng ta cũng sẽ chết hết thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:14.68,Flashback,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Your Lordship, I also told my \Nown children to flee beforehand.}Thưa Ma vương, tôi đã bảo lũ con của mình bỏ trốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:21.94,Italics,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{Not yet...}Vẫn chưa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.64,Italics,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{It's not really over yet.}Vẫn chưa kết thúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.23,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{What do you think you're doing?}Cô nghĩ mình đang làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:31.61,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Isn't it obvious?!}Còn phải hỏi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:36.29,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Your wounds need to be \Ntreated, or you'll die!}Vết thương đó cần chữa trị. Nếu không ngài sẽ chết.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.47,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{You've really taken the whole \N"good person" thing to heart, haven't you?}Cô thực sự là một "người tốt" nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:44.33,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{There's no point, though. \NI weigh over 500 kg.}Nhưng vô ích. Ta nặng đến 500kg.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.79,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Ow...}Đau...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.50,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{Leave me and get out of here.}Kệ ta và đi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:52.98,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{Dying after being flashed by \Na young woman won't be so bad.}Chết trước mặt phụ nữ trẻ không\N mặc sịp cũng không tệ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.96,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Please, stop joking around!}Đừng đùa nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:57.67,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{That's a good reaction.}Phản ứng tuyệt lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:09:00.32,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{You know, after 20 years,}Sau 20 năm,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:02.68,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{my wife still insists we turn the \Nlights out when we go to bed.}vợ ta vẫn bắt tắt đèn khi hành sự.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:06.52,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{Women with some sense of \Nmodesty really are the best.}Quả nhiên phụ nữ xấu hổ là tuyệt vời nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:08.44,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{I've never appreciated \Nthe way Miku does things.}Ta chưa từng thích cách làm của Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.71,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Emperor Takeshita...}Ngài Takeshita...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:15.10,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{You were fighting in a way to avoid the \Nprisoners being hurt in the crossfire.}Ngài đã chiến đấu nhưng cố không lôi chúng tôi vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:18.45,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{You could've taken us as hostages...}Ngài không xem chúng tôi như con tin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.83,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Even now, regardless of what you're saying,}Dù ngay lúc này, những lời ngài nói
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:22.58,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{you're trying to make sure I get to safety.}vẫn chỉ là muốn tôi an toàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.22,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{To me...}Với tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:27.41,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{You don't seem like a bad person.}Ngài không phải kẻ xấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:36.34,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Damn it... I'm not healing fast enough.}Chết tiệt... Không trị liệu kịp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:39.22,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{What the hell's that?}Cái quái gì kia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:43.39,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Emperor Takeshita!}Ngài Takeshita!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:47.39,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{One last word of warning...}Lời cảnh cáo cuối...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:52.20,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{I'm sure you've realized this, \Nbut we're not human.}Chắc cô cũng đã biết. Ta không phải con người.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:54.98,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{Which means there's no hope \Nfor peace between our peoples.}Tức là sẽ không có hòa bình giữa chúng ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:10:01.16,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{Pray all you want, but the human hunts \Nwill resume again, sooner or later.}Hãy cầu nguyện đi, nhưng con người sẽ\N không bao giờ hết bị săn. Chỉ sớm hay muộn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:05.07,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{If you don't want to be caught \Nagain, flee to Hotaena.}Nếu không muốn bị bắt, hãy đến Hotaena.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:10.17,Main,Takeshita,0,0,0,,{Your life's short enough, you should \Nbe able to live it in peace.}Với cuộc sống ngắn ngủi của cô thì ở đó sẽ yên bình.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:13.01,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{What are you saying?}Ngài nói gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:19.25,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Even if you're not human, your concern \Nfor others shows we can coexist...}Dù không phải là con người, thì ngài đã\N cho thấy chúng ta có thể cùng tồn tại...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:28.21,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I am so powerless.}Mình thật vô dụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:31.73,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{When I was attacked...}Khi bị tấn công...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:34.28,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{When I was taken away, and locked up.}Khi bị hãm hiếp, bị nhốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:37.97,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I did nothing myself, I only prayed...}Mình chẳng làm gì ngoài cầu nguyện...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:44.85,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Even though a god came to save us, \Nand was hurt in the process!}Dù thần linh có đến và cứu chúng ta, rồi bị thương!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.64,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,{She has the wrong idea, there.}Cô ấy đã hiểu lầm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:50.62,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{But I can't even carry \Nthe wounded to safety...}Thậm chí mình cũng chẳng\N thể cứu được người bị thương...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:57.35,Italics,Gill,0,0,0,,{Prayer will accomplish \Nnothing. I want power...}Cầu nguyện thật vô ích, mình muốn sức mạnh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:01.43,Italics,Gill,0,0,0,,{The power to protect people, \Nwith my own hands.}Sức mạnh có thể bảo vệ con người.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:05.43,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{If only I had power like that god...}Nếu có sức mạnh như thần linh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:13.98,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,{There are three criteria \Nfor an Idaten manifesting:}Có ba tiêu chí để xuất hiện Idaten:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:18.82,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,{A large volume of thoughts, a long period \Nof time, and a desire for salvation.}Có rất nhiều suy nghĩ, cần nhiều thời gian\N và cầu mong được cứu rỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:24.22,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,{Here in the Zoble Empire, \Nall three criteria have been met.}Ở Zoble này. ba điều kiện đã hội tụ đủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:32.06,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,{And the appearance, sex, name, \Nand personality of an Idaten...}Và ngoại hình, giới tính, tính cách của Idaten...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:37.67,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,{will be based off the most \Npotent source of thoughts,}sẽ dựa vào nguồn suy nghĩ mạnh mẽ nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.17,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,{at the moment of their manifestation.}Tại ngay thời điểm thể hiện ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:46.36,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{What the hell are you doing here?}Cô làm gì ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:53.01,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Um, are you okay? You seem to be hurt.}Cậu ổn chứ? Trông có vẻ đau?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.88,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Is that a joke?! \NYou saw the whole damn thing!}Đùa nhau à? Cô đã xem hết rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:59.11,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I don't know what you mean! You've got \Nthe wrong person! I didn't see anything!}Tôi không biết cậu đang nói gì cả! Nhầm người rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:01.36,Italics,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Shit... my body...}Chết tiệt... cơ thể mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:07.21,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{What was that?!}Vừa rồi là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:09.75,Italics,Hayato,0,0,0,,Tốc độ này... cô ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:12.75,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{I want answers before I kill you.}Trước khi giết thì ta có câu hỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:16.29,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Where is this Demon Lord, Over-M?}Ma vương Over-M đang ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:19.32,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Or is it you?}Hay là ngươi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:23.22,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Demon Lord Over-M? How should I know?}Ma vương Over-M? Sao ta biết?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:27.64,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{You're eight hundred years old, and you \Nexpect me to know something you don't?}Ngay cả người sống 800 năm\N như ngươi còn không biết mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:30.63,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{I might not know him, but he \Nbrings something to mind...}Tuy không biết nhưng ta khá thắc mắc...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:34.36,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{His naming sense reminds me a \Ngreat deal of my Grandfather...}Tên của hắn nhắc ta nhớ về người ông của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:37.72,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{He'd call one demon Super H \Nbecause it was super hard!}Ông ấy gọi một con quỷ rất cứng là Super H!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:41.65,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Or another demon who's weak, cow-like, \Nand preyed upon the others as food,}Còn với mấy con quỷ yếu, hèn nhát, chỉ để làm thức ăn,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:43.40,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,Là Gyudon-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:48.17,Flashback,Obami,0,0,0,,{This seems to be a low-level demon, \Nthe kind that would be used for food...}Có vẻ là một con quỷ cấp thấp để làm thức ăn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:53.04,Flashback,Obami,0,0,0,,{And since he's treated like a disposable \Nsource of food, like a beef bowl,}Và vì là nguồn thực phẩm\N dùng một lần, giống như cơm bò,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:55.29,Flashback,Obami,0,0,0,,{why don't we call him Gyudo-kun?}sao không gọi là Gyudon-kun nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.79,Flashback,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Uh... I don't see why not.}Cũng được...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:01.67,Italics,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Could it really be a coincidence?}Trùng hợp à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:07.87,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Now, this is a fascinating subject. Would \Nyou mind letting me join the discussion?}Ồ, một chủ đề hấp dẫn. Cho ta tham gia với.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.27,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Who are you?!}Ông là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:09.89,Main,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Your Lord—}Ma vu--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.61,Italics,Brandy,0,0,0,,{I should keep quiet, for now.}Mình nên im lặng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:18.65,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Rin, watching you fight stirred some \Nmemories the origins of which I am unsure of.}Rin, xem cô chiến đấu khiến ta\N có những kí ức không rõ ràng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:21.65,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{I just had to speak to you in person.}Nên phải ra nói chuyện trực tiếp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:24.46,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{How do you know my name—}Sao biết tên ta--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:27.32,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{Is that sword the same kind that Sukis used?}Thanh kiếm đó cùng loại với Sukis nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.31,Flashback,Sukis,0,0,0,,{Someone who's as awkward as you,}Đừng bỏ chạy khỏi trận chiến,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:34.89,Flashback,Sukis,0,0,0,,{on top of running from fights, \Ncouldn't produce one of these!}mà thay vào đó hãy tạo ra thứ này!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:38.79,Flashback,Sukis,0,0,0,,{If you're dead set on it, though, \Nswing this one around every day.}Trước sau gì chả chết, hãy vung thứ này mỗi ngày.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:43.96,Flashback,Rin,0,0,0,,{Sukis-san! Stop making fun of me!}Sukis! Đừng có xem thường cháu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:46.06,Flashback,Rin,0,0,0,,{One day, I know I'll...}Một ngày nào đó, cháu sẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:50.39,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{How do you know that?}Tại sao ông biết chuyện đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:57.36,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{I remember you being a frail crybaby, \Nfor some reason, as well.}Ta nhớ cháu từng là một đứa trẻ yếu đuối.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:07.74,Flashback,Rin,0,0,0,,{Grandfather... everyone...}Ông... mọi người...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:13.07,Flashback,Rin,0,0,0,,{Since you've been gone, I've... I've...}Từ khi mọi người đi... Cháu đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:18.09,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Who are you?! How do you know these things?!}Ông là ai? Sao biết chuyện đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:20.71,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{A good question. I have no clue, myself.}Hỏi hay đấy. Ta cũng chẳng rõ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:23.46,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{But I keep remembering more and more...}Nhưng ta cứ liên tục nhớ lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:28.46,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{You would always flee from the demons, \Nbut you hated being alone even more,}Cháu luôn bỏ chạy khi gặp lũ quỷ\N nhưng cũng sợ ở một mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:32.07,Main,Obami,0,0,0,,{so you would insist on heading into battle...}thế nên sẽ lại lao đầu vào chiến đấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:34.22,Flashback,Rin,0,0,0,,{Don't leave me!}Đừng bỏ cháu mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.24,Flashback,Rin,0,0,0,,{I'm going with you!}Cháu đi nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:39.60,Italics,Rin,0,0,0,,{How does he know this?!}Sao ông ta biết?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:44.19,Italics,Brandy,0,0,0,,{She's stopped moving? She's wide open, too.}Dừng di chuyển rồi? Sơ hở.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:48.71,Italics,Brandy,0,0,0,,{During the battle, I came up\N with a way to beat her.}Trong trận chiến mình đã tìm ra cách đánh bại cô ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:50.95,Italics,Brandy,0,0,0,,{But I'll only get one shot at it.}Nhưng chỉ có một cơ hội duy nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:57.05,Main,Decoy,0,0,0,,{Like I said, I have no idea \Nwhere Miku-sama went after that!}Tôi không biết Miku-sama đang ở đâu đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:14:58.85,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{What do you think?}Cô nghĩ sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.56,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{There's only one thing that makes sense.}Chỉ có một điều có thể nghĩ đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:03.64,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{She fled independently, to save her own skin.}Cô ta đã cao chạy xa bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:07.60,Main,Piscalat,0,0,0,,{There'd be no point in interrogating the \Nother demons even if we captured them.}Có thẩm vấn cũng chẳng ích gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.55,Italics,Prontea,0,0,0,,{So, you're saying...}Vậy tức là...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:11.49,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{She managed to escape.}Cô ta đã có thể thoát.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:17.44,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Well, that's unfortunate. I can see now \Nwhy General Piscalat was so wary of her.}Xui thật. Mình muốn tìm hiểu\N tại sao Piscalat lại sợ hãi cô ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:19.48,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{An excellent strategic choice.}Một chiến lược tuyệt vời.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.98,Italics,Neput,0,0,0,,{I've got Biarov and Barcode.}Tôi đã bắt được Biarov và Barcode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:26.92,Main,Barcode,0,0,0,,{G-General Neput... why would you do this?}C-Chỉ huy Neput... tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:27.69,Main,Neput,0,0,0,,{Put a sock in it!}Im đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:30.82,Main,Neput,0,0,0,,{You're gonna go through the same thing, \Nso you'll know exactly why, soon enough.}Sớm muộn ông cũng biết được lý do thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:34.57,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{I see. In that case, \Nhand Barcode over to Prontea-san.}Vậy à? Vậy thì đưa Barcode đến chỗ Prontea đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:38.21,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{As for prime minister Biarov, \Ngive him a brief explanation}Còn thủ tướng Biarov thì giải thích đơn giản thôi,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:40.63,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{and then see to it that he gets to safety.}và đưa ông ta đến nơi an toàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:41.77,Main,Neput,0,0,0,,{Copy that.}Rõ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:45.54,Main,Biarov,0,0,0,,{What exactly is the meaning of this, Neput?}Các người định làm gì, Neput?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.43,Main,Biarov,0,0,0,,{What do you intend on doing with me?!}Ngươi định làm gì ta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:50.52,Main,Neput,0,0,0,,{Once this is over, you're gonna rebuild\N the country for the sake of it's people,}Khi việc này kết thúc, ông sẽ xây dựng\N một quốc gia vì người dân,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:52.05,Main,Neput,0,0,0,,{and the whole world.}và cả thế giới nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:15:58.11,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Hayato's headed this way, too.}Hayato đang đến đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:59.67,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Do you think something happened?}Có chuyện gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.50,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Hey, sorry about the delay.}Xin lỗi vì đã chờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.57,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Here's your Barcode-san.}Barcode đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:08.42,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{It looks like Hayato is headed this way, too... \NDo you have any idea what happened?}Có vẻ Hayato cũng đang quay về... Có chuyện gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:10.99,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Nope. I have a hard time \Nimagining him coming back,}Không, anh không có thời gian quan sát.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.78,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{even if he was on the verge of dying...}Ngay cả khi nó sắp chết...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:13.77,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Where's he at?}Đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:15.21,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Still in this area.}Vẫn ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:16.90,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{That's a bit slow...}Chậm nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:21.17,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Come on. Can't you go a little faster?}Thôi nào, đi nhanh lên đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:25.25,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, no! \NI've never run on water before.}Không được... Tôi chưa từng chạy trên biển.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:27.67,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{What the—?!}Cái--?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:29.60,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{It's fine. She's on our side.}À, bên phe ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:32.97,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Oh, I see! A new Idaten!}Hiểu rồi! Idaten mới nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.29,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{An Idaten?}Idaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:37.52,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{True enough. Zoble did meet all the \Ncriteria for one manifesting...}Không lẽ Zoble đã hội tụ đủ điều kiện?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:41.83,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{I've got surgery to perform. \NPaula, take care of things here.} Thôi, tớ đi phẫu thuật đây. Còn lại cậu lo nhé, Paula.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:43.23,Main,Paula,0,0,0,,{Yeah, got it!}Hiểu rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:45.84,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Hayato, you look like you \Nhad quite a struggle.}Hayato, khá vất vả nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:48.12,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Were you up against Umeyo? Or the Emperor?}Đối thủ là ai? Umeyo? Hoàng đế?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:50.23,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{The Emperor, I think.}Hoàng đế.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.18,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Did you lose?}Thua à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:53.61,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{Man, shut up. I beat him.}Im đi. Đánh bại hắn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:56.46,Main,Hayato,0,0,0,,{I was gonna head back as soon \Nas I handed her off to you guys.}Tôi sẽ quay lại sau khi giao cô ta cho anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:59.49,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{That works out nicely! \NSo, what's your name, new girl?}Đúng lúc đấy. Cô tên gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:03.00,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Uh... Gill. It's Gill!}Gill. Là Gill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:06.04,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Nice to meet you, Gill. I'm Prontea.}Rất vui được gặp cô, tôi là Prontea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.84,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Now, our hands are kind \Nof full with this war...}Lúc này đang trong trận chiến nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:12.34,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Once things calm down a bit, \Nwe'll have a proper chat.}Khi mọi chuyện ổn định, chúng ta sẽ nói chuyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:23.39,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I hope the others were able to escape...}Hi vọng mọi người đã thoát hết...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.43,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:28.48,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Wh-Who are you?! \NWhen did you get behind me?!}A-Anh là ai? Từ khi nào xuất hiện sau lưng tôi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:30.85,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{I kind of wanted to ask that.}Tôi hỏi cô mới hỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:32.86,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Can you warp, or something?}Cô không warp được à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:33.36,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:37.12,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Wait... you are Gill, right?}Ủa? Cô là Gill nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:40.26,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Uh, yes. My name is Gilltina.}Vâng... Tôi là Gilltina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.26,0:17:42.41,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I usually answer to Gill, though...}Tôi cũng hay được gọi là Gill...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.12,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{How do you know my name?}Sao anh biết tên tôi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:47.18,Italics,Prontea,0,0,0,,{A lookalike? And a human?}Y như đúc? Con người à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:50.81,Italics,Prontea,0,0,0,,{The resemblance is too strong \Nfor it to be a coincidence...}Giống nhau quá mức kì lạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.76,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Excuse me, but are you a god—}Xin lỗi nhưng ngài là thần--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:03.52,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{I see. You must've run into Hayato-kun.}Hiểu rồi, cô đi theo Hayato à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:06.31,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{In that case, yes, I'm also a god.}Vậy thì tôi cũng là thần đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:10.27,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{And if you're an ordinary human, \Nthat poses some interesting questions.}Và nếu cô là con người, tôi khá là hứng thú đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:12.27,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{How could you?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:15.82,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{You'd provide a new data sample \Nregarding the manifestation of Idaten.}Cô sẽ là dữ liệu mới về Idaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:18.56,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{How could you do that?!}Tại sao ngài lại làm thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:25.70,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{That's a demon. If I hadn't \Nkilled him, you would've died.}Hắn ta là quỷ đấy. \NNếu không giết thì cô đã chết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:27.66,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{But... still...}Nhưng... vẫn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:30.01,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{To end a life so casually...!}Giết người quá dễ dàng như vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:33.14,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Then would you still criticize \Nme if I were weaker,}Vậy ra nếu tôi yếu hơn
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:38.13,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{and fought a more desperate \Nbattle, but still won?}và chiến đấu giằng co để chiến thắng \Nthì cô sẽ không chỉ trích?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:44.89,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{What exactly would I need \Nto do to satisfy you, then?}Chính xác thì cần phải làm gì để thỏa mãn cô?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:46.21,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I don't know!}Tôi không biết!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:50.35,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I might have died if you hadn't killed him...}Tôi có thể chết nếu ngài không giết anh ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:54.40,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{But... taking an enemy's \Nlife so one-sidedly...}Nhưng... cướp đi mạng sống dễ dàng như thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.90,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I just can't bear the sight of it!}Tôi chỉ là không chịu nổi thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:02.68,Italics,Prontea,0,0,0,,{She's an interesting human, but her \Npersonality is pretty intensely troublesome.}Cô ta là con người thú vị nhưng tính cách lại phiền phức.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:04.84,Italics,Prontea,0,0,0,,{So, what should I do?}Làm gì đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:06.58,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{I'm sure that with the war,}Tôi chắc rằng với trận chiến này,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:10.17,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{there are many who were unable \Nto escape, due to injuries...}có rất nhiều người đã không thể thoát...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:14.03,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{But I'm unable to help them by myself.}Nhưng tôi lại không thể làm gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:15.95,Main,Gill,0,0,0,,{Please, god, grant me your—}Xin thần linh hãy--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:20.93,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Better to have her sleep \Nuntil everything's over.}Nói nhiều quá, ngủ chút đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:24.80,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{I doubt any style of warfare \Nwould satisfy your conscience.}Có chiến đấu thế nào thì cũng chẳng\N thỏa mãn lương tâm của cô đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.43,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Ignorance is bliss.}Điếc không sợ súng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:31.70,Italics,Rin,0,0,0,,{His memories are patchy... there's \Nnot much of a resemblance, either.}Kí ức mờ ảo... nhân dạng không đúng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:35.15,Italics,Rin,0,0,0,,{But he knows things only \NGrandfather could know...}Nhưng hắn biết những điều mà chỉ ông biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:39.94,Italics,Rin,0,0,0,,{And there are little \Nhabits that are the same.}Và có những thói quen giống ông.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:45.10,Main,Rin,0,0,0,,{Is that you, Grandfather?!}Là ông sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:52.04,Italics,Brandy,0,0,0,,{As powerful as your attacks are, \Nyour defense is terrible!}Đòn tấn công cũng mạnh và phòng thủ cũng khủng!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:55.71,Italics,Brandy,0,0,0,,{It's so bad that even using a little \Nof your own strength against you}Tuy hơi hèn khi lợi dụng chính sức mạnh của ngươi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.42,Italics,Brandy,0,0,0,,{makes a limb fly off!}lấy từ cái chi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:00.42,Italics,Brandy,0,0,0,,{You can't even withstand the \Nimpact of your own attacks!}Ngươi sẽ không chịu nổi đòn tấn công từ chính bản thân!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:04.80,Italics,Brandy,0,0,0,,{Now, have a taste of one \Nof those attacks, and die!}Giờ thì ta đã có cơ hội, chết đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:15.32,Italics,Brandy,0,0,0,,{That was way stronger than I expected... \NI accidentally blew the Demon Lord away.}Uy lực khủng quá... mình lỡ thổi bay luôn ma vương rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:19.09,Italics,Brandy,0,0,0,,Ngài ấy là robot mà... chắc sẽ ổn thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:23.45,Italics,Brandy,0,0,0,,{But I need to strike again... \Nneed to get rid of her or—}Nhưng phải phản công... ngay khi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:37.50,Italics,Rin,0,0,0,,{Oh, Grandfather...}Ông...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.76,Italics,Rin,0,0,0,,{I've missed you... for so long...}Cháu nhớ ông... nhiều lắm..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:44.79,Italics,Rin,0,0,0,,{Could we be... together again?}Liệu chúng ta... có thể gặp nhau nữa không?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:50.77,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{Master?}Sư phụ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.12,0:20:54.49,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,{Six hours after Takeshita \Nand Brandy were defeated,}Sáu tiếng sau khi Takeshita và Brandy bị đánh bại,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:57.52,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,{Piscalat and Cory joined the assault.}Piscalat và Cory tham chiến.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.40,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,{Hayato would return to the front lines,}Hayato trở lại chiến trường,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:03.65,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,{and Barcode would take over \Noperations from Piscalat.}và Barcode tiếp nhận phòng quan sát từ Piscalat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.91,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,{Barcode was able to locate \Nthe remaining demons,}Barcode đã tìm ra tàn quỷ còn sót lại,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:09.01,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,{which Prontea and Hayato then eliminated.}Prontea và Hayato xử lý chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:13.41,Narration,Narr,0,0,0,,{The war was, effectively, over.}Kết thúc chiến tranh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:20.33,Main,Miku,0,0,0,,{Looks like we're starting \Nover from scratch, huh?}Có vẻ chúng ta lại Zero kara hajimeru.
